titleStmt.title: Five vvonders seene in England. [brace] Two at Barnstable, one at Kirkham, one in Cornwall, one in Little Britain in London. In all which places whereby Gods judgements are miraculously seene upon some. Severall miraculous accidents have hapned to the amazement of all those that have beene eye-witnesses thereof.

editionStmt.edition: The second impression with additions, and certificate from those who were eye witnesses thereof. Published according to order.

notesStmt.note: Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
